			<node ID="ID_1218622223" TEXT="ROG Strix GeForce&#174; RTX 2080 OC edition 8GB GDDR6 made for driving 4K display resolution and VR. Spanning 2.7-slots the ROG Strix GeForce&#174; RTX 2080 keeps Turing&#8482; chilled with a massive heatsink Axial-tech fans and MaxContact technology." />
