			<node ID="ID_735695280" TEXT="WAN Wide Area Network#$D$#">
		<node ID="ID_401176465" LINK="https://www.lifewire.com/wide-area-network-816383" TEXT="What Is a Wide Area Network (WAN) and How Does It Work?">
			<node ID="ID_1685641289" TEXT="A WAN (wide area network) is a communications network that spans a large geographic area such as across cities states or countries. They can be private to connect parts of a business or they can be more public to connect smaller networks together." />
