		<node ID="ID_1537096665" LINK="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/network-devices-hub-repeater-bridge-switch-router-gateways/" TEXT="Network Devices (Hub Repeater Bridge Switch Router ">
			<node ID="ID_1104013945" TEXT="7. Brouter &#8211; It is also known as bridging router is a device which combines features of both bridge and router. It can work either at data link layer or at network layer. Working as router it is capable of routing packets across networks and working as bridge it is capable of filtering local area network traffic. References" />
			</node>
