			<node ID="ID_1370338287" TEXT="HDLC vs PPP | difference between HDLC and PPP. This page on HDLC vs PPP describes basic difference between HDLC and PPP protocols.. We know that unlike LAN which is used in a single organization WAN is used to connect different organizations across the cities and countries." />
