			<node ID="ID_576447210" TEXT="Short for Carrier Sense Multiple Access/Collision Avoidance a network contention protocol that listens to a network in order to avoid collisions unlike CSMA/CD that deals with network transmissions once collisions have been detected. CSMA/CA contributes to network traffic because before any real data is transmitted it has to broadcast a signal onto the network in order to listen for " />
