			<node ID="ID_624870150" TEXT="Welcome to the heart of networking: the routing protocols. We begin our series of looks at these protocols with one of the originals and the most simple: RIP the Routing Information Protocol. RIP like all routing protocols is designed to disseminate network information pertinent to routers. At " />
