		<node ID="ID_1729332906" LINK="http://carroll.net/blog/dynamic-routing-with-redhat/" TEXT="Dynamic Routing with Redhat &#187; CarrollNet">
			<node ID="ID_1449812965" TEXT="RIP Routing with RHEL. As a network becomes more complex the need to distribute routing information automatically becomes apparent. Without automation anytime a router or Internet connection fails engineers need to visit an ever increasing number of devices in the network to manually adjust routing tables." />
