			<node ID="ID_1258898018" TEXT="Routing in MANET : Introduction. In any network whenever data transmission occurs it is done through a series of nodes that are connected from source to destination. The shortest path to transmit the data from source to destination is called as route and this process is called as routing.Discovering the shortest route among a mobile ad-hoc " />
