			<node ID="ID_1710526455" TEXT="Transport layer offers peer-to-peer and end-to-end connection between two processes on remote hosts. Transport layer takes data from upper layer (i.e. Application layer) and then breaks it into smaller size segments numbers each byte and hands over to lower layer (Network Layer) for delivery. Functions. This Layer is the first one which " />
