			<node ID="ID_134218057" TEXT="transport layer (networking) (Or host-host layer) The middle layer in the OSI seven layer model. The transport layer determines how to use the network layer to provide a virtual error-free point to point connection so that host A can send messages to host B and they will arrive un-corrupted and in the correct order. It establishes and dissolves " />
