			<node ID="ID_1112749090" TEXT="TCP vs UDP. This page on TCP vs UDP describes difference between TCP and UDP.Both protocols sit on layer-4(Transport layer) of the OSI layer just above the IP layer. Unlike TCPUDP is connectionless and provides no reliability no windowing and no funtion to ensure data is received in the same order as it was transmitted." />
