			<node ID="ID_520901380" TEXT="TCP and UDP aren&#8217;t the only protocols that work on top of IP. However they are the most widely used. How TCP Works. TCP is the most commonly used protocol on the Internet. When you request a web page in your browser your computer sends TCP packets to the web server&#8217;s address asking it to send the web page back to you." />
