			<node ID="ID_1849508384" TEXT="User Datagram Protocol (UDP) was introduced in 1980 and is one of the oldest network protocols in existence. Its a simple OSI transport layer protocol for client/server network applications is based on Internet Protocol (IP) and is the main alternative to TCP." />
