			<node ID="ID_1066484566" TEXT="Application (Layer 7) OSI Model Layer 7 supports application and end-user processes. Communication partners are identified quality of service is identified user authentication and privacy are considered and any constraints on data syntax are identified. Everything at this layer is application-specific." />
			</node>
