			</node>
		<node ID="ID_78453327" LINK="https://study.com/academy/lesson/application-layer-of-the-osi-model-definition-functions-protocols.html" TEXT="Application Layer of the OSI Model: Definition Functions ">
			<node ID="ID_1179900372" TEXT="The Application Layer is where we find the final pieces necessary to accomplish these tasks. The Application Layer is the ending of data transfer. When you get here you will find applications " />
			</node>
