			<node ID="ID_213494307" TEXT="That&#8217;s where application layer security and the OSI model come into the picture. What is the OSI Model? The Open Systems Interconnection or OSI Model is a security framework which sets out recommendations for application security in terms of seven layers (three media and four host layers) all of which must be secured for an application to " />
			</node>
